  <brief_title>Vasopressin to Prevent Hypotension During Beach Chair Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Trials of Vasopressin for Prevention of Hypotension During Shoulder Surgery in Beach Chair Position Under General Anesthesia</official_title>
